<view class="big-box data-v-165bdf4a"><view class="background data-v-165bdf4a"></view><view class="content data-v-165bdf4a"><view class="top-box data-v-165bdf4a"><view class="cell-item data-v-165bdf4a"><view class="label data-v-165bdf4a">WiFi名称</view><input placeholder="请输入WiFi名称" placeholder-class="placeholder" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','wifiName','$event',[]],['formData']]]]]}}" value="{{formData.wifiName}}" bindinput="__e" class="data-v-165bdf4a"/></view><view class="cell-item data-v-165bdf4a"><view class="label data-v-165bdf4a">WiFi密码</view><input placeholder="请输入WiFi密码" placeholder-class="placeholder" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','wifiPwd','$event',[]],['formData']]]]]}}" value="{{formData.wifiPwd}}" bindinput="__e" class="data-v-165bdf4a"/></view></view><view class="explain data-v-165bdf4a"><view class="text data-v-165bdf4a">{{"热点名称:"+hotspot}}</view></view><view class="bottom-box data-v-165bdf4a"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['hotspotSet']]]]}}" class="bottom-btn data-v-165bdf4a" bindtap="__e">生成热点名称</view><block wx:if="{{hotspot}}"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['copyHotspot']]]]}}" class="bottom-btn data-v-165bdf4a" bindtap="__e">复制热点名称</view></block></view><view class="explain data-v-165bdf4a"><view class="text data-v-165bdf4a">1.复制生成的热点名称设置为手机热点并开启</view><view class="text data-v-165bdf4a">2.重启设备即可配置成功</view><view class="text data-v-165bdf4a">注：iPhone的热点名称在设置-通用-关于本机-名称,</view><view class="text data-v-165bdf4a">W89型号的WiFi锁需进入配网模式。</view></view></view></view>